pick the knife up from the counter
turn right and move forward to the window, then turn left
slice the lettuce into smaller pieces
put the knife on the counter

turn left and move forward to the end of right-side counter, then turn left and face the sink
place the lettuce into the sink and wash the lettuce off with water, then turn the water off and pick the lettuce up

open the refrigerator, place the lettuce inside, and then close the refrigerator

Walk across the room and walk in to the sink counter.
